                <p>1. You must read, agree with, and accept all of the terms and conditions contained or referenced in these Terms of Service including, our Privacy Policy, and any of our other applicable terms, conditions, or policies before you sign up for an Account or use our Service (collectively, the “Additional Terms”).</p>
